parameters:
\SE[16]Right? My lover is strong, aren't they? \SE[0]I wonder...?
Is it okay for us to have a victory?

\SE[60]... What? I will... return Mama to you. \SE[45] There's no
longer... any use for me... right...?

\SE[59]I saw a glimpse of your past self from the other Alice.
\!\SE[54]
\SE[57]That child... once again, on their own...
\SE[59]... So? Do you think you understand everything about me?

\SE[0]No, I don't really understand you. \!\SE[59]...But there's
one thing I want to tell you.

\SE[23]Your name is... 'Claudia'. \SE[54] 'Mama' couldn't tell
you... the important... gift...

\SE[51]Thank you, Laura. \SE[50]I think that child... was saved,
even if just a little.
\SE[46]... Let's go home. To our house....

\SE[7] It seems like I've used too much magic power from here....
I can't maintain my form anymore, I'm crumbling. \SE[8]... That's
why I have to escape... but...
\SE[52]Where is the exit... Do you know?

\SE[64]I-I don't know but...! \.We have no choice but to go back
the way we came...!?
\SE[12]Y-Yes, that's right...! F-For now, let's go...!
